                </svg>
                Contactar por WhatsApp
            </a>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 mt-8">
                <a href="mailto:danielpemor123@gmail.com" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
                    Email
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/daniel-perez-8007b3328/" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors" target="_blank">
                    LinkedIn
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/danielpemor" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors" target="_blank">
                    GitHub
                </a>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mt-8">
                © 2024 Daniel Pérez. Desarrollando el futuro, un proyecto a la vez.
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.11.4/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.11.4/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>